text: The following television stations in the United States brand as channel 3 (though neither using virtual channel 3 nor broadcasting on physical RF channel 3): * KBJR-DT2 in Duluth, Minnesota * KESE-LP in Yuma, Arizona * KESQ- TV in Palm Springs, California * KRII-DT2 in Chisholm, Minnesota * News-Press 3 NOW in St. Joseph, Missouri * WMDT-DT2 in Salisbury, Maryland * WSEE-DT2 in Erie, Pennsylvania 03 branded
title: Channel 3 branded TV stations in the United States
